    text: 
    lines:
    - When I was young, the galaxy was alive with sound.
    - "Every world sang its own song \u2014 oceans hummed, cities echoed with symphonies,
      and even the stars pulsed to the rhythm of life."
    - "We didn\u2019t just listen to music \u2014 we lived inside it."
